Motormaster smiles, and lowers his mouth towards the comm-link of
Astroblast, "I want you to lead a Decepticon assault force to this
destination" he then gives it in code to Cyclonus, "Take Skullgrin,
Speedbreaker, Drag Strip, and Scourge, while the rest of us lick our
wounds. You are in command for this" Motormaster says, then he turns,
"Astroblast, how much longer?"
